API practice

API practice#

This is where I will be practice producing API called maps.

from ipyleaflet import *
import json


#make the map
m = Map(center=(50,-120), zoom=6, basemap = basemaps.Esri.DeLorme)

#add the layers
with open('test.geojson') as f:
    data = json.load(f)

geo = GeoJSON(data=data,
              style = {
                'color': 'blue'
              })

m.add_layer(geo)
